Text: Detta är ju en enda stor mp3-fil. Hur gör jag för att dela upp den i låtar?
Ladda hem Goldwave (eller Soundforge). Där kan du sätta in splitpunkter mellan låtarna och sen dela upp skivan automatiskt! Jättebra när man rippar vinyl också...

This is NOT an ALBW. 
If it was, ya could have split it with
AlbaExtractor0.4-dev or AlbumWrap_Extractor_1.0.

Sorry for the inconvenience....

This has nothing do with STANLEY CLARKE/AL DI MEOLA/JEAN-LUC PONTY • The Rite of Strings (1995) as the Mp3 tags and subject indicate

Its probably just a standard compilation bought at a petrol station.
It's mostly live, without public sound, and starts with standards as Persuasion ,Black Magic Woman, Incident At Neshabur, but mixs in the end with some obscure 80
Nothing to download in my opinion...
These 14 tracks are from Best Of Santana, Vol. 2
